{"title":"采煤","authors":["景椿　春蛟"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"采煤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西山煤矿通讯组  景椿  春蛟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你打锤，我把钎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮——当，叮——当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锤一锤往里钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钎把稳，锤打准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕煤壁硬又坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装火药，点引线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰，当，哗啦……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满洞尽是烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着烟往里钻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一筐一筐背入罐，（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼，噜，噜，噜，噜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推到下把钩。（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当电铃响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镐车滚滚转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摘钩挂钩不迟延，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装罐笼更不慢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一班出他二百四十罐！（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注（一）罐——煤车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注（二）下把钩——井下停车场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注（三）一班——八小时二百四十罐，合一百四十四吨。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}